Summary: two "stars" split and travelled off in "V" formation
divs: Sighting DetailsJust sitting out in the yard and I saw two faint small "stars" which were moving.. then they suddenly separated and moved apart in a "V" formation.. at the speed of a passing satelitte, i.e. not super fast. But strange movements for "stars" I checked "human space sightings" website and there were NO reported passing sateelittes overhead, at least for another 40 minutes and these did not act like satelittes passing overhead..split in "V" formation. Happened between 10 pm and 10:03 pm on May 24, 2011 in Dandridge, TN
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Dandridge
There were no other sightings in Dandridge on or around May 24th 2011
